{"word":"James","slug":"james","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>James</b> 1. An apostle<br/> - Son of Zebedee and Salome<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=21'>Mat 4:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=56'>Mat 27:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=40'>Mar 15:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=16&verse=1'>Mar 16:1</a> <br/> - Brother of John, and a fisherman<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=10'>Luk 5:10</a> <br/> - Called to be an apostle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=22'>Mat 4:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=2'>Mat 10:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=20'>Mar 1:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=14'>Luk 6:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=13'>Act 1:13</a> <br/> - Surnamed Boanerges by Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=17'>Mar 3:17</a> <br/> - An intimate companion of Jesus, and present with Him:<br/> b at the great draught of fish<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=5&verse=10'>Luk 5:10</a><br/> b at the healing of Peter's mother-in-law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=29'>Mar 1:29</a><br/> b at the raising of the daughter of Jairus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=5&verse=37'>Mar 5:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=51'>Luk 8:51</a><br/> b at the transfiguration of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=1'>Mat 17:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=2'>Mar 9:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=28'>Luk 9:28</a><br/> b in Gethsemane<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=37'>Mat 26:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=33'>Mar 14:33</a><br/> - Asks Jesus concerning His second coming<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=13&verse=3'>Mar 13:3</a> <br/> - Bigotry of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=9&verse=54'>Luk 9:54</a> <br/> - Civil ambitions of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=20&verse=23'>Mat 20:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=41'>Mar 10:41</a> <br/> - Present at the Sea of Tiberias when Jesus revealed Himself to the disciples after His resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=21&verse=2'>Joh 21:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=7'>1Co 15:7</a> <br/> - Martyred<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=2'>Act 12:2</a> <br/> 2. An apostle, son of Alphaeus<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=3'>Mat 10:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=3&verse=18'>Mar 3:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=15'>Luk 6:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=13'>Act 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=17'>Act 12:17</a> <br/> 3. Brother of Jesus<br/> - Identified as a brother of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=55'>Mat 13:55</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=3'>Mar 6:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=1&verse=19'>Gal 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=56'>Mat 27:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=10'>Luk 24:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=9'>Gal 2:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=12'>Gal 2:12</a> <br/> - The brother of Judas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=6&verse=16'>Luk 6:16</a>; <a href='B:'></a> <br/> - The brother of Joses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=40'>Mar 15:40</a> <br/> - Witness of Christ's resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=15&verse=7'>1Co 15:7</a> <br/> - Addresses the council at Jerusalem in favor of liberty for the Gentile converts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=21'>Act 15:21</a> <br/> - Disciples sent by, to Antioch<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=12'>Gal 2:12</a> <br/> - Hears of the success attending Paul's ministry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=19'>Act 21:19</a> <br/> - Epistle of James<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=1&verse=1'>Jas 1:1</a> "}]}